<% data = adapter.panel_data %>
## Polymarket Conditional Tokens

Outcome-token ledger (ERC-1155) on Polygon. Records every market's outcome
shares; resolution payouts are paid out here.

<% if data[:errors].present? %>
_Some reads failed: <%= data[:errors].map { |k, v| "#{k} (#{v})" }.join(", ") %>._
<% end %>

<% if data[:resolutions].present? %>
### Recently resolved

<% data[:resolutions].each do |res| %>
- **<%= res.market_label %>** — payouts [<%= res.payouts.join(", ") %>]<% if res.slug %> (`<%= res.slug %>`)<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if data[:preparations].present? %>
### Recently prepared (new markets)

<% data[:preparations].each do |prep| %>
- **<%= prep.market_label %>** — <%= prep.outcome_slot_count %> outcomes<% if prep.slug %> (`<%= prep.slug %>`)<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if data[:redemptions].present? %>
### Recent redemptions

<% data[:redemptions].each do |redeem| %>
- <%= redeem.redeemer %> redeemed<% if redeem.payout %> $<%= number_with_delimiter(redeem.payout.round(2)) %><% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if data[:resolutions].blank? && data[:preparations].blank? && data[:redemptions].blank? %>
_No CTF activity in the last ~3h._
<% end %>
